        "creation_date": 1541324415,
        "body": "<p>You can specify the name of the package by configuring the jar plugin:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;plugin&gt;\n    &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;\n    &lt;artifactId&gt;maven-jar-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n    &lt;version&gt;3.1.0&lt;/version&gt;\n    &lt;configuration&gt;\n        &lt;finalName&gt;ready_release/my-project&lt;/finalName&gt;                   \n    &lt;/configuration&gt;\n&lt;/plugin&gt; \n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>This will create the jar file at <code>&lt;project-root&gt;/target/ready_release/jar-name.jar<\/code> and every subsequent build will overwrite it.<\/p>\n",
        "answer_id": 53139445,
        "question_id": 53139396
    }],
